Both the restore and re-create data disaster recovery options require standing up a new <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>, which can take hours. If you require shorter RTO, several options involving a pre-created standby hardware and <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> are available. The following table outlines these options:

